<section>
  <h2>NOTES</h2>
  <p><sup>1</sup> There are experts who claim that certain companies in Spain have perverted the true concept of the term advergaming by creating products of dubious technical quality, incapable of complying with the basic objectives of communication. This has been one of the main barriers to growth for the sector in the country, together with the lack of knowledge regarding the medium itself.</p>
  <p><sup>2</sup> To be fair, this is the case with all forms of advertising.</p>
